de.ityx.mediatrix.data

Class Project

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.ityx.mediatrix.data.ErpsData
      • de.ityx.mediatrix.data.Project
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IErpsData, IViewFilterDefinition, Serializable

    public class Project
extends ErpsData
implements IViewFilterDefinition
    The project contains the entity of all logical linked subprojects. All created customers are assigned to the project. Projects can be related to each other per alias. It's a logical path to manage same customers under different projects(e.g. to show all the cases from a customer in different projects).
